Validus Holdings Ltd. (VR) ,the reinsurer
that bought IPC Holdings Ltd., said  Michael Moore  was hired to
served as chief accounting officer.  Moore, who will report to the company’s chief financial
officer, joins from Axis Capital Holdings Limited where he
served as senior vice president, corporate operations, according
to a regulatory filing today from Bermuda-based Validus.  To contact the reporter on this story:
